title: Flamingpear.Flexify.v1.99.for.Adobe.Photoshop.Incl.Keygen
description:
Version 1.99 adds six new projections including stereographic and Lagrange.

Plus: 16-bit color. Over sixty projections including origami, Omnimax&reg;, Lego&reg; plans, cube maps, and a spikeball. One-click to iPhoto. Sharpening and polyhedron options. Make LDraw files . Export polyhedron faces. Fifteen kinds of input including equirectangular, polar, mirror ball, cylindrical, orthographic, Mollweide, fisheye, globe-gores, and tiles.
